Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:05.92,FairyTail BDF,,0,0,0,,                                  お こく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:10.58,FairyTail BD,,0,0,0,,{\i1}人口１，７００万の永世中立国。{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:10.58,FairyTail BDF,,0,0,0,,         じん こう                       まん えいせいちゅうりっこく       
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.96,FairyTail BD,,0,0,0,,{\i1}そこは　魔法の世界。{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.96,FairyTail BDF,,0,0,0,,                    ま ほう       せ かい  
